Get the price order from offer in Remitano
Using api (api.remitano.com/api/v1/markets/{currency_pair}/order_book)

{currency_pair} pair of crypto and base currency. Ex: BTCVND, ETHVND...
- Base currency is VND
- Crypto currencies are BTC, ETH, LTC, BCH, XRP, USDT (can be extended later)

Result will show best bids and best asks price (json format)


Programming language: Python
Lib: Requests